# Frontend environment — Vite
# The React app has NO server-side secrets.
# All API keys (Anthropic, GitHub, DB) live in backend/.env only.
#
# Vite's built-in BASE_URL is set automatically by the build tool;
# no manual configuration is needed for local development.
#
# Only add variables here if you introduce custom VITE_ prefixed vars.
# Example:
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8000
